    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Seriously, it's been pampered since day one, always kept in a climate-controlled garage, and it still has that fresh new-car smell! It's in truly stunning shape\u2014not a mark on it and it drives like an absolute dream. If you've been looking for a ride that's basically brand new but at a much better value, you've found it. I\u2019d love for you to come see it in person because it looks even better than the photos!",
