      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty! It has been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, you'd think it was brand new\u2014not a single blemish to be found. It drives like a total dream and is just waiting for someone to take it on its next adventure. I\u2019m so excited for whoever gets to take this home!",
