      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade FD3S RX-7, showcasing an impeccably maintained 13B-REW power plant with flawless sequential turbocharger transition. This specimen retains its original longitudinal front-midship layout, delivering a perfect 50/50 weight distribution. The chassis remains rigid, complemented by factory double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential that ensures surgical cornering precision. Recent compression tests confirm optimal apex seal integrity across all rotors. The five-speed manual gearbox offers crisp gate engagement with no synchro grind. This is a turn-key example of rotary engineering at its zenith, free of vacuum leak gremlins or thermal degradation.",
